subject: Track and Field
Pole Vault
lead_paragraph: Walt Henning, a native of South Huntington, N.Y., and a sophomore at Louisiana State, set a meet record of 72 feet 8 ½ inches in winning the 35-pound weight throw at the Collegiate Invitational at the New Balance Track and Field Center in Manhattan. Renaud Lavillenie, a college student in France, set a meet record in the pole vault at 18-8 1/4.
